# PRODUCTS API

### Get all products
GET /products HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8888
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get product by ID
GET /products/1 HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8888 

Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create product
POST /products/1 HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8888 
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop",
  "description": "Gaming laptop",
  "images": "image.jpg",
  "rating": 4.5,
  "stock": 10
}

###

### Update product
PATCH /products/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Laptop Gaming RTX",
  "description": "Gaming laptop RTX series",
  "images": "image2.jpg",
  "rating": 4.8,
  "stock": 8
}

###

### Delete product
DELETE /products/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json